<h1 id="IDEs_with_introspection-based_code_completion_.2For.2F_integrated_debugger">IDEs with introspection-based code completion /or/ integrated debugger</h1>
<span class="anchor" id="line-51"></span><span class="anchor" id="line-52"></span><span class="anchor" id="line-53"></span><span class="anchor" id="line-54"></span><div><table><tbody><tr>  <td style="vertical-align: top"><p class="line891"><strong>Name</strong> </td>
  <td style="vertical-align: top"><p class="line891"><strong>Platform</strong> </td>
  <td style="vertical-align: top"><p class="line891"><strong>Updated</strong> </td>
  <td style="vertical-align: top"><p class="line891"><strong>Notes</strong> </td>
</tr>
<tr>  <td style="vertical-align: top"><span class="anchor" id="line-55"></span><p class="line891"><a href="/moin/Komodo">Komodo</a> </td>
  <td style="vertical-align: top"><p class="line862">Windows/Mac/Linux </td>
  <td style="vertical-align: top"><p class="line862">2012 </td>
  <td style="vertical-align: top"><p class="line891"><a class="http" href="http://www.activestate.com/komodo-edit">Komodo Edit</a> (open source, as part of the <a class="http" href="http://www.openkomodo.com">Open Komodo</a> project). Little brother to Komodo IDE. </td>
</tr>
<tr>  <td style="vertical-align: top"><span class="anchor" id="line-56"></span><p class="line891"><a href="/moin/BlackAdder">BlackAdder</a> </td>
  <td style="vertical-align: top"><p class="line862">Windows/Linux </td>
  <td style="vertical-align: top"><p class="line862">2004 </td>
  <td style="vertical-align: top"><p class="line862">Commercial; integrated debugger; interfaces with Qt Designer </td>
</tr>
<tr>  <td style="vertical-align: top"><span class="anchor" id="line-57"></span><p class="line891"><a href="/moin/eric">eric</a> </td>
  <td style="vertical-align: top"><p class="line862">Python + <a href="/moin/PyQt">PyQt</a> + QScintilla </td>
  <td style="vertical-align: top"><p class="line862">2008 </td>
  <td style="vertical-align: top"><p class="line862">Open Source, interfaces with Qt Designer, Qt Linguist, unittest; integrated debugger </td>
</tr>
